net.proteusframework.core.xml

Class GenericParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
      • org.xml.sax.ext.DefaultHandler2
        • net.proteusframework.core.xml.GenericParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ContentHandler, DTDHandler, EntityResolver, ErrorHandler, DeclHandler, EntityResolver2, LexicalHandler

    public class GenericParser
extends DefaultHandler2
    XML parser that fires actions for registered tags. It also outputs content that doesn't match the specified tags to a PrintWriter.
    Author:
    Russ Tennant (russ@i2rd.com)
